<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <%- include('./partials/head') %>
  <title>Garçon Baguette | Contacter</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/contact.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-dark text-white">
  <header>
    <%- include('./partials/navbar', { pageTitle: 'Contacter' }) %>
  </header>

  <form method="POST" action="/contact/?lang=fr">
    <div class="container mt-5 mb-5 d-flex justify-content-center">
      <div class="card bg-dark px-5 py-5">
        <h1 class="text-center">Contactez-moi</h1>
        <p class="text-center">N'hésitez pas à utiliser le formulaire ci-dessous pour me contacter. Je vous répondrai dans les meilleurs délais.</p>
        <div class="row mt-3">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <label for="name" class="form-label">Votre Nom</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="name" placeholder="Nom" required>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <label for="email" class="form-label">Votre Courriel</label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="nom@email.com" required>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <label for="subject" class="form-label">Sujet</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" name="subject" placeholder="Sujet" required>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <label for="message" class="form-label">Votre Message</label>
          <textarea rows="6" class="form-control" name="message" placeholder="Message" required></textarea> 
        </div> 
        <button id="submit-button" class="btn mt-5" type="submit">Envoyer le Message <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right ml-2 mt-1"></i></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </form>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.10.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-7+zCNj/IqJ95wo16oMtfsKbZ9ccEh31eOz1HGyDuCQ6wgnyJNSYdrPa03rtR1zdB" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-QJHtvGhmr9XOIpI6YVutG+2QOK9T+ZnN4kzFN1RtK3zEFEIsxhlmWl5/YESvpZ13" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>